	   <tr><td colspan=2>i suggest you head to Frontier Mts and grp or even charm kite giants there. not so good xp, but its hell lvl, although the loot is good. and if you get some rare drops (ex. forest loops, strawspun belt, legchopper, and many more weps) there all yours&nbsp;&nbsp;=)  you can make VERY good money off them whether soloing or grping. i highly suggest that place. my second recommendation would be the SplitPaw Lair. some good drops but most Fine Steel weps. xp however is good for hell lvl. i went there when i just felt like i wanted outta lvl 30  =)  then my third choice would be The Overthere. one zone off of Frontier Mts its full of wandering mobs including kunark rhinos, more sarnaks, cacti, cats, and cockatrices. xp was exceptionally well there and i stayed there till i was outta hell. up to you, if you want money head to giants in Frontier Mts. if your more inclined for the xp, yet want some good loot, head to SplitPaw Lair (its in South Karana btw). if you just wanna get outta hell, The Overthere is the zone for you. hope that helped<br><br>Taamas Starsinger<br>31st Season<br>House of Wargoth<br>Saryrn<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
