	   <tr><td colspan=2>From what I have gather trying to learn my bard, instruments is only require when the effect happen "Ie: when it says "A Something winces". So, play a song using weapon, before the message shows up, change to an instrument (secondary hand) and when the effect happens, switch back to a weapon .. all requires timing :-) ... <br><br>or you can increase your H2H by using only instrument and punching them or just sing the song and use a weapon. Only some song requires you to use instruments.:-).<br><br> Mind you I am only so far level 20 and still learning to be a bard, but so far, he is by far my most fav. always doing something instead of staring into a BOOK!. hehe :-).<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
